Unlock your own inner genius using ChatGPT as a structured thinking partner.

“Act as a mind-mirroring partner. I’ll brain-dump my idea stream. You reflect back themes, potential value, and counter-intuitions.”

“Run a 3-part brainstorm with me: 1) Expand the idea wildly, 2) Trim the excess ruthlessly, 3) Package it as a product, framework, or offer.”

“Use divergent thinking to generate 10 creative solutions to this mundane problem I’ve normalized.”

“Ask me one provocative question. Based on my answer, ask another — keep going until I land on something I’ve never thought before.”

“Design a personal ‘ideation dojo’ — 7 questions I can journal on weekly to build a habit of original thinking.”
